    note right of CauseUnset
        initCause() can be called at most once.
        Cause not yet initialized via constructor.
    end note

    note right of CauseSet
        initCause() is forbidden here.
        Throws IllegalStateException if called.
        Cause was set via constructor or initCause().
    end note

    note right of maybeCauseSet
        Protected constructor: cause may or may not
        be set depending on runtime parameter value.
        initCause() is speculatively allowed.
    end note
